<H4><I>News of people, development, research, and applications from the leaders in ocean optics and data systems.</I></H4>
</CENTER><HR>
<A NAME="list"></A><H2>News Index</H2>

<OL><OL>
<LI><A HREF="#Newsa">CI INTRODUCES ITS NEW FASTRACKA FLUORIMETER</A><BR>
<LI><A HREF="#Newsb">OCEANOLOGY INTERNATIONAL '97, 12-14 MAY 1997, WORLD TRADE CENTRE, SINGAPORE</A><BR>
