<FONT SIZE="4">
<UL>
<LI>Conductivity, temperature, depth and fluorescence as standard<BR>
<LI>Chlorophyll<I>-a</I> rhodamine-B, and nephelometer options available<BR>
<LI>Solid state memory and/or real-time data transmission internal batteries and/or externally powered<BR>
