<TITLE> Lab Policies </TITLE>

<BODY  BACKGROUND=frost.gif>
<CENTER>
<H1>Lab Policies</H1>
</CENTER>

<UL>
<LI> No food or beverages are allowed in the lab.
<LI> The lab may be used anytime the Transportation building
     is open to the public.
<LI> Do not use your own floppy disks in the lab PC's (we
     have had many virus problems in the past).
<LI> Do Not remove lab manuals from the lab.
<LI> The Transportation Building is open Tuesday, Wednesday and
	Thursday from 6:30 to 10 p.m., and on Sunday from noon until 3 p.m.
</UL>

