<title>Just a reminder....</title>

<h1>
Just a reminder....

<H2>
<p>
<p>
<p>
<p>
This triple world is dreadful as that of a burning house, overwhelmed with a number of evils, entirely inflamed on every side by a hundred different sorts of birth, old age and disease.<p>
<p>
<p>
<p>
<p>
<p>

<p>					{--  a common Buddist viewpoint}
