Record</A> published by the <A HREF="http://www.cup.cam.ac.uk/">
Cambridge University Press</A>
<LI><A HREF=wdcc.htm>The ICSU World Data Centre C (Glaciology)</A>
<ul>
 <li>WDC C also hosts the <A HREF="scar/wwg.htm">SCAR Working Group
on Glaciology</A> home page
