<H1>Scott Polar Research Institute</H1>  
<hr>
<CENTER><H2>So you want to Search the World-Wide Web?</H2>
</CENTER>
<hr>
<H3>Here are some links to some amazing "Search Engines":</H3>
<B>University of Cambridge</B> <A HREF="http://www.cam.ac.uk/Searching/index.html#netwide">WebSearch 
Page</A>, which includes AltaVista, Lycos and Webcrawler.
<P>


