Muscat, Cambridge, or use the 
<A HREF="http://index-me.spice.co.uk/ferret/textonly.html">text-only 
version</A> 

<LI><a href="http://www.search.com/">Comprehensive Search Engine (USA)</a> 
with links to almost every other search engine and index

