<p>

<h2>FORTHCOMING PUBLICATIONS</h2>

<p>

<b>Books</b>

<p>

<a href="keyguide.htm">Keyguide to information sources on the polar and cold 
regions</a>. (Co-author with P. Speak). London: Mansell. (due 1997)

<p>

<b>Conference papers</b>

<p>

Antarctica Retrospective - a comprehensive resource for the history of Antarctica and the 
Southern Ocean. In: C. Innes-Taylor et al, eds. Creativity, Lighting the Poles: Collaborative 
Solutions to Common Needs. Proceedings of the 16th Polar Libraries Colloquy. 
Anchorage: University of Alaska Anchorage, Consortium Library.

<p>

The Library of the Scott Polar Research Institute as a resource for the study of polar 
tourism. In: B. Stonehouse, ed. Management of polar tourism: proceedings of the conference
held at the Scott Polar Research Institute, Cambridge, 19-21 August, 1996.

