<DOCNO>WT02-B08-286</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA021-000219-B022-167</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://tethys.jpl.nasa.gov:80/Annette/nearrealtime/nrt_ssa.html 128.149.33.75 19970107091039 text/html 1815
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
