<BODY BGCOLOR="#ffffff" LINK="#0000ff" VLINK="#ff0000" ALINK="#ff0000" TEXT="#000000" >
<H1>Factors that Contribute to Sea Surface Height</H1>
<p>
<font size= +1>
Except for gravity, each changes over days, months, or a few years. Of these remaining factors, basin-wide ocean circulation is the most stable - it does not change significantly over periods of days or months.
</font>
<p>
