<H1>Global Ocean Dynamic Topography</H1>
<p>
<font size = +1>
The difference between the highest and lowest parts of ocean dynamic topography is just over 2 meters (6 feet); from about -120 centimeters to +100 centimeters.
</font>
<p>
<h5>
