<H1>Ocean Dynamic Topography Compared to the Geoid</H1>
<p>
<font size = +1>
The <i> overall  </i> change in sea surface height caused by circulation is about 75 times less than that due to gravity. <a href=images/geoid.gif>Click here</a> to see a smoothed model of the Earth's Geoid.
</font>
<p>
