<h5 align=center>THE CANADIAN RESEARCH COMMITTEE ON TAXATION - LE COMITE CANADIEN DE RECHERCHES SUR LA TAXATION</h5>
<p align=center><strong>Head Office/Siege Social</strong><br>
</p>
<div align=center><center>
<address>P.O. BOX 49193, 7275 Sherbrooke St. East<br>
Montreal, PQ. H1N 3T6<br>
